title: House on the Lake
posting_body: Cozy home on a peaceful (no-motor) lake.
Burien is a young city about 10-minutes outside of Seattle, Washington.
It has 6 miles of coastline, unique restaurants, and neighborhood bars.
Around our corner is Olde Burien- gelato, library, intimate restaurants, chill at the local bar.
Minutes from Seatac Airport, Seattle (15 minutes), Pike Place Market, Pioneer Square, Waterfront, West Seattle.
Take the local light rail into the city!
